name: Cathay Pacific Cargo 747-8F [B-LJL] Close Up Taxi and Takeoff from Calgary Airport
description:
What a sight! Here we have Cathay Pacific Cargo's 747-8 Freighter taxiing super close up and departing runway 17L on a hot summer morning. I'd been hoping to catch a 747 from up close like this for a long time and was very happy to see it turning my way on Bravo! ATC is included, hope you enjoy.

Thanks for watching!
